    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――NEXT VENUSグランプリの予選を控えたある日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "—One day‚ ahead of the preliminary round\nof the NEXT VENUS Grand Prix",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 1.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（今日は星見市主催の野外イベント当日だ）\n（若手注目グループとしてサニピも参加している）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Today’s the day of the outdoor event staged by Hoshimi City.)\n(Sunny Peace is participating as a rookie group in the spotlight.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.466666666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3266.6666666666656,
          "startTime": 12.733333333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hillpark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 12.733333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_01-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "あ、{user}さ～ん！\n大変です！　見て下さい、これ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh {user}-san…!\nIt’s terrible! Just look at this!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hillpark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 20.366666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "どうした、そんなに慌てて……ん！？\nどこか体が震えているような……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What happened? What’s the rush?\nYou seem to be trembling…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.166666666666668,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hillpark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 24.333333333333332
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_01-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "そうなんです！\nさっきから全然治まらなくって……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yep! Sure did!\nI’ve been like this a while‚ and it’s not getting better!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.933333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hillpark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 28.766666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "緊張してるのか？\nそれにしては妙に嬉しそうだけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Are you nervous?\nYou see kind of happy though.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.733333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hillpark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 33.56666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_01-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "えへへ……はい\n全然、緊張とかじゃないんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hee hee… Yes.\nI’m not nervous at all.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.733333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hillpark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 38.36666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_01-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "自分でもびっくりしてるんですけど\nたぶんこれ、武者震いってやつかなーって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s surprising even me‚\nbut maybe I’m just trembling with excitement.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.93333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_01-skr005.m4a",
      "text": "これからステージに立つんだって思ったら\n胸がドキドキワクワクしてきちゃって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When I think about how I’m going to be up on stage‚\nmy heart starts racing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hillpark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 50.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_01-skr006.m4a",
      "text": "よーし、やるぞー！　って噛み締めたら\nびっくりするぐらい震えてきちゃったんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When I tell myself “let’s do this!” and get into it‚\nI tremble so much it’s shocking.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.63333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "なるほど、そういうことか……安心したよ\nよっぽど今日のステージが楽しみなんだな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So that’s how it is… That’s a relief.\nYou’re really looking forward to today’s show.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.86666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hillpark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 62.733333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_01-skr007.m4a",
      "text": "はい！　だって\nデビューした時と同じステージで歌えるんですよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh yes! I mean‚\nI can sing on the same stage as I did for my debut.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_01-skr008.m4a",
      "text": "なんだか、ただいまーっ！\nって気持ちで一杯なんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m filled with a feeling\nkind of like going home!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hillpark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 72
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "いいな、その「ただいま」という言葉\nその気持ち、お客さんに届けてみよう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "“Going home‚” that’s a good way to put it.\nTry to show the crowd that’s how you feel.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.93333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_01-skr009.m4a",
      "text": "そうですね。届くといいなぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ it’d be nice if they can learn how I feel.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.36666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hillpark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 81.73333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_01-skr010.m4a",
      "text": "あっ、そろそろ出番なので……\n行ってきます、{user}さん！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ I’m on soon…\nWish me luck‚ {user}-san!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.96666666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2266.6666666666656,
          "startTime": 86.23333333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "（どんなライブもデビューライブのように）\n（新鮮に感じられるのかもしれないな）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Maybe every show has that fresh feel)\n(of a debut performance for her.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 92.2
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 92.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_01-skr011.m4a",
      "text": "今日は野外イベントに来ていただいて\n本当にありがとうございます！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you so much for coming\nto today’s outdoor show!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.06666666666666,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-out-01.m4a",
          "delay": 166.6666666666714,
          "startTime": 96.23333333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_01-skr012.m4a",
      "text": "私、サニーピースの川咲さくらっていいます！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m Sakura Kawasaki of Sunny Peace!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.53333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 102.73333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_01-skr013.m4a",
      "text": "今日はデビューしたステージでまたライブ出来るので\nすっごくワクワクしていました！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Today I’m back on the same stage where I debuted‚\nso I’m just so excited!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 108.56666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_01-skr014.m4a",
      "text": "私、このステージ大好きなんです！　風が気持ち良くて\n海も見えて、こんなに青空が広がって！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I love this stage! The breeze feels nice‚\nI can see the sea‚ and the blue sky’s so huge!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_01-skr015.m4a",
      "text": "デビューライブに来てくれた方も、そうでない方も\n一緒に楽しんでくれたら嬉しいでーす！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Whether or not you were here for my debut‚\nI’ll be happy if we can all enjoy this together!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.63333333333334,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-out-01.m4a",
          "delay": 766.6666666666657,
          "startTime": 122.4
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 125.46666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_01-skr016.m4a",
      "text": "それじゃ、いきますよー！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ let’s do this!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.46666666666667,
      "sfxList": [
